Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Gunnoe.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Gunnoe (1997), 79 Ohio St.3d 191.]

(No. 97-435 Submitted April 16, 1997 Decided July 16, 1997.) *192Geoffrey Stem, Disciplinary Counsel, Cynthia L. Roehl and Sally Ann Steuk, Assistant Disciplinary Counsel, for relator. Gerald E. Gunnoe, pro se. Per Curiam.

Upon review of the record, we adopt the findings, conclusion, and recommendation of the board. Respondent is hereby publicly reprimanded. Costs are taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
